      • RData

        public RData(byte[] rawData,
             int start,
             int length)
        Construct this Resource Record data object with the provided raw byte data, start index, and length in bytes.
        Assumes the input data is encoded correctly with an RData object at index start.
        Parameters:
        rawData - The raw data to parse as an RData object.
        start - The byte index to start parsing at.
        length - The length in bytes of this RData object in raw byte format.
